So I was fortunate.

00:33:47.790 --> 00:33:49.740 align:middle line:84%
Because I felt that
I was going to have

00:33:49.740 --> 00:33:51.060 align:middle line:90%
to move out of San Francisco.

00:33:51.060 --> 00:33:53.580 align:middle line:90%
This was my home of 30 years.

00:33:53.580 --> 00:34:00.060 align:middle line:84%
And I was sent the book called
"Shungite" by Regina Martino,

00:34:00.060 --> 00:34:01.472 align:middle line:90%
by my publisher.

00:34:01.472 --> 00:34:02.350 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:34:02.350 --> 00:34:04.260 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: So
you see, here they're

00:34:04.260 --> 00:34:05.850 align:middle line:90%
working with me on my book.

00:34:05.850 --> 00:34:07.830 align:middle line:84%
And they're sending
me the information

00:34:07.830 --> 00:34:08.739 align:middle line:90%
that I need further.

00:34:08.739 --> 00:34:09.719 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: From hers.

00:34:09.719 --> 00:34:10.677 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Exactly.

00:34:10.677 --> 00:34:12.163 align:middle line:84%
So you see how
life is reciprocal.

00:34:12.163 --> 00:34:13.199 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:34:13.199 --> 00:34:15.726 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: And we
earn what we receive.

00:34:15.726 --> 00:34:17.850 align:middle line:84%
We receive the
information that we're

00:34:17.850 --> 00:34:20.699 align:middle line:84%
supposed to receive, for
our work, for the work.

00:34:20.699 --> 00:34:22.230 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: So how did you feel?

00:34:22.230 --> 00:34:26.130 align:middle line:84%
What did you experience once
you had this in your field?

00:34:26.130 --> 00:34:30.960 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: I felt that
it helped me tremendously

00:34:30.960 --> 00:34:36.659 align:middle line:84%
with the pain that I was feeling
in my actual brain, when they

00:34:36.659 --> 00:34:39.150 align:middle line:90%
first turned on the signal.

00:34:39.150 --> 00:34:43.320 align:middle line:84%
They turned on a citywide
signal in San Francisco

00:34:43.320 --> 00:34:48.570 align:middle line:90%
on New Year's Day of 2014.

00:34:48.570 --> 00:34:50.850 align:middle line:84%
And they WiFi'd
Market Street, which

00:34:50.850 --> 00:34:55.469 align:middle line:84%
is near to where my apartment
is, for several miles,

00:34:55.469 --> 00:34:56.910 align:middle line:90%
straight down to the water.

00:34:56.910 --> 00:34:57.615 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Wow, I
didn't know about this.

00:34:57.615 --> 00:34:58.415 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Yes.

00:34:58.415 --> 00:35:02.760 align:middle line:84%
And when this happened,
I felt as though my aura

00:35:02.760 --> 00:35:05.430 align:middle line:90%
was being shattered.

00:35:05.430 --> 00:35:12.480 align:middle line:84%
And I began to-- I began to have
pain, real pain, in my brain,

00:35:12.480 --> 00:35:14.790 align:middle line:90%
like I had never had before.

00:35:14.790 --> 00:35:18.420 align:middle line:84%
And I also was having trouble
remembering my dreams.

00:35:18.420 --> 00:35:21.900 align:middle line:90%
I had a very active dream life.

00:35:21.900 --> 00:35:25.800 align:middle line:84%
And I began to
realize that I wasn't

00:35:25.800 --> 00:35:32.160 align:middle line:84%
able to have that as a
tool, as fully in my life,

00:35:32.160 --> 00:35:34.290 align:middle line:90%
as I did before.

00:35:34.290 --> 00:35:39.060 align:middle line:84%
So all these things are
a process of experience,

00:35:39.060 --> 00:35:43.599 align:middle line:84%
of learning, a cause and effect,
the effect behind the cause.

00:35:43.599 --> 00:35:44.640 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: So you're here.

00:35:44.640 --> 00:35:45.720 align:middle line:90%
You're going through.

00:35:45.720 --> 00:35:47.396 align:middle line:84%
You feel like your
aura's shattered.

00:35:47.396 --> 00:35:48.395 align:middle line:90%
Your brain is shattered.

00:35:48.395 --> 00:35:51.810 align:middle line:84%
And you come in contact with
this through the publisher.

00:35:51.810 --> 00:35:53.972 align:middle line:90%
What happened?

00:35:53.972 --> 00:35:55.680 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Oh,
after I read the book,

00:35:55.680 --> 00:35:58.920 align:middle line:90%
I sought out the shungite.

00:35:58.920 --> 00:36:04.680 align:middle line:84%
And I did order shungite
from the author of the book

00:36:04.680 --> 00:36:05.530 align:middle line:90%
in Paris.

00:36:05.530 --> 00:36:11.194 align:middle line:84%
And so the healing
necklace came.

00:36:11.194 --> 00:36:12.610 align:middle line:84%
There was something
for my-- there

00:36:12.610 --> 00:36:13.900 align:middle line:90%
was a disk for the cell phone.

00:36:13.900 --> 00:36:16.050 align:middle line:10%
There was a disk
for the computer.

00:36:16.050 --> 00:36:20.320 align:middle line:84%
And I felt like I was able
to balance out more with it.

00:36:20.320 --> 00:36:23.340 align:middle line:10%
And it helped with the pain.

00:36:23.340 --> 00:36:25.680 align:middle line:90%
And that was good.

00:36:25.680 --> 00:36:31.300 align:middle line:10%
And I just felt that it also
helped me to-- at night,

00:36:31.300 --> 00:36:35.610 align:middle line:10%
when I sleep, if I
can't get to sleep,

00:36:35.610 --> 00:36:41.430 align:middle line:10%
because I feel like I have such
erratic energy around my head,

00:36:41.430 --> 00:36:42.285 align:middle line:10%
from the WiFi--

00:36:42.285 --> 00:36:43.530 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: From the
WiFi and everything.

00:36:43.530 --> 00:36:45.130 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: --I
take the necklace

00:36:45.130 --> 00:36:48.300 align:middle line:90%
and I put it right here.

00:36:48.300 --> 00:36:50.197 align:middle line:84%
And I fall asleep
in about 10 minutes.

00:36:50.197 --> 00:36:51.280 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Oh, that's good.

00:36:51.280 --> 00:36:52.680 align:middle line:90%
So it really does seem to help.

00:36:52.680 --> 00:36:54.180 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: It
does seem to help.

00:36:54.180 --> 00:36:58.420 align:middle line:10%
However, the signal
is increasing.

00:36:58.420 --> 00:37:00.670 align:middle line:84%
So as the signal
has increased, I've

00:37:00.670 --> 00:37:04.800 align:middle line:84%
had to get more
shungite around my bed.

00:37:04.800 --> 00:37:07.460 align:middle line:90%
And I've had to arm up--

00:37:07.460 --> 00:37:08.800 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right, right.

00:37:08.800 --> 00:37:10.890 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: --suit up.

00:37:10.890 --> 00:37:11.800 align:middle line:90%
And--

00:37:11.800 --> 00:37:12.883 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: To deal with it.

00:37:12.883 --> 00:37:15.580 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Thank god
we have these beautiful--

00:37:15.580 --> 00:37:16.380 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:37:16.380 --> 00:37:19.860 align:middle line:84%
And these technologies,
such as this and others,

00:37:19.860 --> 00:37:21.930 align:middle line:84%
have-- they were known
in ancient times.

00:37:21.930 --> 00:37:24.340 align:middle line:84%
We didn't trash our
brain voluntarily

00:37:24.340 --> 00:37:28.230 align:middle line:84%
and disrespect ourselves the
way we did, the way we do now.

00:37:28.230 --> 00:37:29.830 align:middle line:84%
And there was one
example in your book

00:37:29.830 --> 00:37:33.930 align:middle line:84%
that I found interesting, which
was a thawed out man, about

00:37:33.930 --> 00:37:36.420 align:middle line:84%
5,000 years old, who
had been suspended,

00:37:36.420 --> 00:37:39.130 align:middle line:84%
who had this tattoo
strategically placed.

00:37:39.130 --> 00:37:40.840 align:middle line:84%
And you're saying
that that tattoo

00:37:40.840 --> 00:37:43.030 align:middle line:90%
was for a very specific use.

00:37:43.030 --> 00:37:44.910 align:middle line:84%
It was a type of
technology of the day.

00:37:44.910 --> 00:37:45.960 align:middle line:90%
Let's talk about that.

00:37:45.960 --> 00:37:46.780 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Yes.

00:37:46.780 --> 00:37:52.060 align:middle line:84%
In the 5000-year-old--
I guess it was a mummy,

00:37:52.060 --> 00:37:57.090 align:middle line:84%
the mummy named
Otzi-- he had tattoos

00:37:57.090 --> 00:38:01.110 align:middle line:84%
over his arthritic joints,
the areas of his body

00:38:01.110 --> 00:38:05.070 align:middle line:84%
where it was found that
his bones were arthritic.

00:38:05.070 --> 00:38:12.130 align:middle line:10%
And this segues into the
science of BioGeometry

00:38:12.130 --> 00:38:18.930 align:middle line:10%
that Dr. Ibrahim Karim of Egypt
has developed BioSignatures

00:38:18.930 --> 00:38:27.670 align:middle line:10%
and ways of creating energy
frequencies with art and design

00:38:27.670 --> 00:38:28.680 align:middle line:10%
work.

00:38:28.680 --> 00:38:30.480 align:middle line:10%
So these are other
ways that we can

00:38:30.480 --> 00:38:37.770 align:middle line:10%
begin to incorporate healing
frequencies, to counter

00:38:37.770 --> 00:38:40.020 align:middle line:10%
the dissonant frequencies.

00:38:40.020 --> 00:38:43.630 align:middle line:84%
And it's imperative
that companies

00:38:43.630 --> 00:38:47.400 align:middle line:90%
begin to apply these ways.

00:38:47.400 --> 00:38:49.830 align:middle line:90%
We can make technology safer.

00:38:49.830 --> 00:38:54.670 align:middle line:84%
There's no reason why it
should be so destructive.

00:38:54.670 --> 00:38:55.490 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:38:55.490 --> 00:39:00.130 align:middle line:84%
So now this sets us onto-- let's
go back to consciousness, away

00:39:00.130 --> 00:39:02.750 align:middle line:90%
from these healing technologies.

00:39:02.750 --> 00:39:04.630 align:middle line:84%
And one of the
statements you make

00:39:04.630 --> 00:39:06.960 align:middle line:84%
in this book, which is
interesting-- you say,

00:39:06.960 --> 00:39:10.420 align:middle line:84%
people have been misled to
create their own reality.

00:39:10.420 --> 00:39:13.510 align:middle line:84%
And from there we're going
to go into the processes,

00:39:13.510 --> 00:39:15.820 align:middle line:84%
through the principles you
talk about-- universal mind,

00:39:15.820 --> 00:39:18.480 align:middle line:84%
and so forth-- of coming
into connection with self.

00:39:18.480 --> 00:39:20.760 align:middle line:84%
And it's different for
everybody, of course.

00:39:20.760 --> 00:39:24.720 align:middle line:84%
I mean, creating our
own reality is virtually

00:39:24.720 --> 00:39:27.010 align:middle line:84%
a mantra in the
New Age community.

00:39:27.010 --> 00:39:31.680 align:middle line:84%
So let's look at your take on
creating one's own reality.

00:39:31.680 --> 00:39:35.380 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Well to look at
what's happening in the world

00:39:35.380 --> 00:39:39.170 align:middle line:10%
right now, in regard to
creating your own reality,

00:39:39.170 --> 00:39:44.070 align:middle line:10%
you have to take into account
the different types of ego

00:39:44.070 --> 00:39:47.670 align:middle line:10%
that we work with.

00:39:47.670 --> 00:39:51.780 align:middle line:84%
In my work, I have
studied that there

00:39:51.780 --> 00:39:55.110 align:middle line:84%
are the pure ego-- we
have the pure ego, which

00:39:55.110 --> 00:39:58.410 align:middle line:84%
is the part of the ego
that knows that it exists.

00:39:58.410 --> 00:40:01.020 align:middle line:10%
It's the pure consciousness.

00:40:01.020 --> 00:40:08.320 align:middle line:84%
It's the part of the ego that
actually lives beyond the body.

00:40:08.320 --> 00:40:09.400 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:40:09.400 --> 00:40:12.880 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: And then
you have the intellect.

00:40:12.880 --> 00:40:16.570 align:middle line:10%
The intellect functions
on a more linear level.

00:40:16.570 --> 00:40:19.990 align:middle line:84%
And the intellect is
very closely connected

00:40:19.990 --> 00:40:24.340 align:middle line:84%
with what's called the false
ego-- or the dispirited ego

00:40:24.340 --> 00:40:27.440 align:middle line:84%
is probably a better
way to describe it.

00:40:27.440 --> 00:40:32.010 align:middle line:10%
So the dispirited or
false ego, we see,

00:40:32.010 --> 00:40:40.390 align:middle line:10%
plays very much a part
of influencing people

00:40:40.390 --> 00:40:44.320 align:middle line:10%
into believing that they
create their own "reality."

00:40:44.320 --> 00:40:50.910 align:middle line:84%
In fact, reality is created by
universal law, by natural law,

00:40:50.910 --> 00:40:54.895 align:middle line:84%
by the invisible energies
that underpin existence.

00:40:54.895 --> 00:40:57.400 align:middle line:90%


00:40:57.400 --> 00:41:01.600 align:middle line:10%
We create our own
reality, either

00:41:01.600 --> 00:41:05.480 align:middle line:10%
working-- there's two ways
to create your own reality.

00:41:05.480 --> 00:41:07.930 align:middle line:10%
You can either create
your own reality

00:41:07.930 --> 00:41:12.940 align:middle line:10%
by connecting the intellect
with the soul, the higher

00:41:12.940 --> 00:41:15.700 align:middle line:10%
self of the soul.

00:41:15.700 --> 00:41:17.900 align:middle line:10%
And you can create
your own reality

00:41:17.900 --> 00:41:24.634 align:middle line:10%
by choosing to align with spirit
and do the work of spirit.

00:41:24.634 --> 00:41:26.800 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And you create
your own reality by default

00:41:26.800 --> 00:41:28.120 align:middle line:90%
by doing neither of the above.

00:41:28.120 --> 00:41:28.920 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Yes.

00:41:28.920 --> 00:41:32.380 align:middle line:84%
Or you create your own
reality by really believing

00:41:32.380 --> 00:41:35.770 align:middle line:84%
that you create your
own reality and not

00:41:35.770 --> 00:41:43.390 align:middle line:84%
taking universal law, cosmic
mind into the equation,

00:41:43.390 --> 00:41:45.820 align:middle line:84%
and believe that--
I'm going to give you

00:41:45.820 --> 00:41:50.290 align:middle line:84%
a perfect example of what we're
doing right now with creating

00:41:50.290 --> 00:41:52.340 align:middle line:90%
our own reality.

00:41:52.340 --> 00:41:55.840 align:middle line:10%
We are using the false ego
to create our own reality.

00:41:55.840 --> 00:41:58.300 align:middle line:90%
I was having lunch one day.

00:41:58.300 --> 00:42:00.880 align:middle line:84%
I overheard a lady
and a gentleman.

00:42:00.880 --> 00:42:03.490 align:middle line:10%
And she had just taken
one of these classes

00:42:03.490 --> 00:42:05.260 align:middle line:10%
about creating your own reality.

00:42:05.260 --> 00:42:08.440 align:middle line:10%
And she started talking
to her companion

00:42:08.440 --> 00:42:13.570 align:middle line:10%
about how her uncle
had-- was so wealthy.

00:42:13.570 --> 00:42:15.430 align:middle line:90%
And he was so old.

00:42:15.430 --> 00:42:17.650 align:middle line:90%
And she was so poor.

00:42:17.650 --> 00:42:21.130 align:middle line:10%
And her idea of
creating her own reality

00:42:21.130 --> 00:42:23.530 align:middle line:10%
was to encourage
her uncle to pass

00:42:23.530 --> 00:42:25.464 align:middle line:10%
so that she could have the--

00:42:25.464 --> 00:42:26.380 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Inheritance.

00:42:26.380 --> 00:42:28.340 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: --the
wealth, the inheritance.

00:42:28.340 --> 00:42:33.190 align:middle line:10%
And when I heard that, I
just thought, how awful.

00:42:33.190 --> 00:42:36.700 align:middle line:90%
What an awful reality is that?

00:42:36.700 --> 00:42:37.930 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:42:37.930 --> 00:42:39.513 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Because
you're creating

00:42:39.513 --> 00:42:41.710 align:middle line:10%
a frequency, a
dissonant frequency,

00:42:41.710 --> 00:42:46.450 align:middle line:10%
not only for yourself, by
wishing that for yourself,

00:42:46.450 --> 00:42:49.410 align:middle line:10%
but for wishing that
for someone else.

00:42:49.410 --> 00:42:51.310 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly, yeah

00:42:51.310 --> 00:42:54.130 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: And that that's
the simplest way that I can--

00:42:54.130 --> 00:42:56.770 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, it's the lowest
aspect of egoic function.

00:42:56.770 --> 00:43:00.850 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Yes, and
so look, let's make sure

00:43:00.850 --> 00:43:05.050 align:middle line:10%
that what we're saying, when
we say that we're creating

00:43:05.050 --> 00:43:08.320 align:middle line:10%
our own reality, that
what we're saying

00:43:08.320 --> 00:43:14.170 align:middle line:10%
is that we're not attempting
to override the higher

00:43:14.170 --> 00:43:18.070 align:middle line:10%
intelligence that
underlies existence.

00:43:18.070 --> 00:43:19.660 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right, exactly.

00:43:19.660 --> 00:43:22.720 align:middle line:84%
So now let's get into
soul Breathing itself

00:43:22.720 --> 00:43:25.630 align:middle line:84%
and some of the ways
in which-- let's

00:43:25.630 --> 00:43:29.570 align:middle line:84%
start at really basic entry
points, where people can say,

00:43:29.570 --> 00:43:30.370 align:middle line:90%
it's true.

00:43:30.370 --> 00:43:33.610 align:middle line:84%
I really need to make a
conscious effort and practice

00:43:33.610 --> 00:43:34.720 align:middle line:90%
of connecting to self.

00:43:34.720 --> 00:43:39.630 align:middle line:84%
Because A, it can easily
perform miracles on your behalf.

00:43:39.630 --> 00:43:40.570 align:middle line:90%
They're not miracles.

00:43:40.570 --> 00:43:42.320 align:middle line:84%
It's just doing what
it's already designed

00:43:42.320 --> 00:43:43.840 align:middle line:90%
to do, without encumbrance.

00:43:43.840 --> 00:43:44.640 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Yes.

00:43:44.640 --> 00:43:47.230 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And B, you can
have a much clearer idea

00:43:47.230 --> 00:43:49.810 align:middle line:84%
of where your energies, and
talents, and skills should

00:43:49.810 --> 00:43:54.010 align:middle line:84%
be placed, in any
given incarnation.

00:43:54.010 --> 00:43:59.110 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE:
Yes, I mean when we

00:43:59.110 --> 00:44:05.290 align:middle line:10%
are able to-- all the
advanced masters will tell you

00:44:05.290 --> 00:44:11.440 align:middle line:10%
that it's not them that creates
the, quote, unquote, miracle.

00:44:11.440 --> 00:44:15.920 align:middle line:10%
It's the higher
aspect of the self.

00:44:15.920 --> 00:44:19.810 align:middle line:84%
It's the surrendering
of the self.

00:44:19.810 --> 00:44:21.310 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: To its
own higher aspect.

00:44:21.310 --> 00:44:22.570 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Yes.

00:44:22.570 --> 00:44:27.587 align:middle line:84%
And so this is a
humbling experience.

00:44:27.587 --> 00:44:32.536 align:middle line:90%


00:44:32.536 --> 00:44:36.490 align:middle line:10%
This is probably
the greatest gift

00:44:36.490 --> 00:44:39.970 align:middle line:10%
that anyone could
be given in life,

00:44:39.970 --> 00:44:48.520 align:middle line:10%
is to connect with this
deep, high master within.

00:44:48.520 --> 00:44:50.530 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:44:50.530 --> 00:44:57.070 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: It exceeds
any monetary number

00:44:57.070 --> 00:45:03.700 align:middle line:10%
that we could place
upon any material item.

00:45:03.700 --> 00:45:06.070 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:45:06.070 --> 00:45:08.530 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: And the
reason is because once you

00:45:08.530 --> 00:45:16.030 align:middle line:10%
begin to resonate
with your soul self,

00:45:16.030 --> 00:45:19.180 align:middle line:10%
money becomes
almost unnecessary.

00:45:19.180 --> 00:45:23.310 align:middle line:90%
Because you're taken care of.

00:45:23.310 --> 00:45:25.310 align:middle line:10%
You're carried.

