You're carried in a higher way.

00:45:28.350 --> 00:45:31.050 align:middle line:10%


00:45:31.050 --> 00:45:38.880 align:middle line:10%
Things begin to become more
harmoniously patterned.

00:45:38.880 --> 00:45:43.680 align:middle line:10%
And the downward spiral
of depression and illness,

00:45:43.680 --> 00:45:52.460 align:middle line:10%
confusion, war, destruction--
they don't enter

00:45:52.460 --> 00:45:54.590 align:middle line:10%
into the equation anymore.

00:45:54.590 --> 00:45:55.580 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:45:55.580 --> 00:45:59.390 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Because
you're incapable-- addiction.

00:45:59.390 --> 00:46:02.900 align:middle line:84%
Ah, when you reach
a certain frequency,

00:46:02.900 --> 00:46:05.510 align:middle line:90%
you can't be addicted.

00:46:05.510 --> 00:46:11.910 align:middle line:10%
You cannot get to a higher
frequency if you're addicted.

00:46:11.910 --> 00:46:12.710 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:46:12.710 --> 00:46:14.085 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: It
doesn't allow--

00:46:14.085 --> 00:46:16.190 align:middle line:10%
it keeps you in a
certain frequency,

00:46:16.190 --> 00:46:19.770 align:middle line:10%
and doesn't allow you to evolve.

00:46:19.770 --> 00:46:20.570 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:46:20.570 --> 00:46:22.550 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: To advance.

00:46:22.550 --> 00:46:26.900 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And there
are many forces that,

00:46:26.900 --> 00:46:28.970 align:middle line:84%
whether it's intentional
or not, keep us

00:46:28.970 --> 00:46:32.960 align:middle line:84%
from taking this step into
companionship with ourselves,

00:46:32.960 --> 00:46:34.640 align:middle line:84%
not the least of which
are those charged

00:46:34.640 --> 00:46:37.790 align:middle line:90%
with our spiritual development.

00:46:37.790 --> 00:46:40.820 align:middle line:84%
I know that you, as
Barbara Hand Clow has

00:46:40.820 --> 00:46:42.800 align:middle line:84%
done in her recent
work of fiction,

00:46:42.800 --> 00:46:44.277 align:middle line:90%
do talk about the effects.

00:46:44.277 --> 00:46:45.110 align:middle line:90%
What do you call it?

00:46:45.110 --> 00:46:46.700 align:middle line:90%
The sorcerers.

00:46:46.700 --> 00:46:50.420 align:middle line:84%
The sorcerers out of the
Vatican and what they do

00:46:50.420 --> 00:46:51.695 align:middle line:90%
in their planetary influence.

00:46:51.695 --> 00:46:53.500 align:middle line:84%
And let's talk about
that for a moment.

00:46:53.500 --> 00:46:55.310 align:middle line:84%
Barbara's written one
and is in the process

00:46:55.310 --> 00:46:58.130 align:middle line:84%
of writing another book
about-- it's a work of fiction,

00:46:58.130 --> 00:47:01.520 align:middle line:84%
but it's telling the
true facts and principles

00:47:01.520 --> 00:47:04.850 align:middle line:84%
about what is going on in those
realms with the Vatican church

00:47:04.850 --> 00:47:08.720 align:middle line:84%
and how it's expressing
in the world.

00:47:08.720 --> 00:47:13.430 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Well it's
a very delicate subject

00:47:13.430 --> 00:47:15.230 align:middle line:90%
for many people.

00:47:15.230 --> 00:47:17.210 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: It is.

00:47:17.210 --> 00:47:20.480 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: But
I think that when

00:47:20.480 --> 00:47:27.290 align:middle line:10%
you consider that there is no
other country in the world that

00:47:27.290 --> 00:47:33.830 align:middle line:10%
doesn't have to pay
taxes, or is not audited,

00:47:33.830 --> 00:47:37.370 align:middle line:10%
you connect that with the
IRS, you see the connection,

00:47:37.370 --> 00:47:42.500 align:middle line:10%
you connect it with the banks,
you connect it with the world

00:47:42.500 --> 00:47:46.340 align:middle line:10%
financial systems that
we have in place now,

00:47:46.340 --> 00:47:52.190 align:middle line:10%
and you just begin to realize
that there's something

00:47:52.190 --> 00:47:54.310 align:middle line:10%
not quite right about it!

00:47:54.310 --> 00:47:56.220 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:47:56.220 --> 00:48:01.910 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: And so
it's OK to recognize

00:48:01.910 --> 00:48:04.796 align:middle line:90%
that you're being bamboozled.

00:48:04.796 --> 00:48:07.310 align:middle line:90%


00:48:07.310 --> 00:48:12.920 align:middle line:10%
And the illusion of
what has been created

00:48:12.920 --> 00:48:20.780 align:middle line:10%
through the centuries have
basically-- it's a form of mind

00:48:20.780 --> 00:48:24.560 align:middle line:10%
control, is what it is.

00:48:24.560 --> 00:48:29.450 align:middle line:84%
And then you have the people
who insist that religion is

00:48:29.450 --> 00:48:33.350 align:middle line:84%
hallowed ground, that
it cannot be questioned,

00:48:33.350 --> 00:48:43.040 align:middle line:84%
that it cannot be talked
about in a way that is honest.

00:48:43.040 --> 00:48:48.030 align:middle line:90%
It's not acceptable to do it.

00:48:48.030 --> 00:48:51.620 align:middle line:84%
And so when you begin
to understand more,

00:48:51.620 --> 00:48:52.940 align:middle line:90%
you become more conscious.

00:48:52.940 --> 00:48:56.120 align:middle line:84%
You begin to recognize and
you begin to see everything

00:48:56.120 --> 00:48:58.700 align:middle line:90%
for exactly what it is.

00:48:58.700 --> 00:49:03.020 align:middle line:84%
And I really feel
that people are

00:49:03.020 --> 00:49:07.290 align:middle line:84%
being led away from the
inner religious experience--

00:49:07.290 --> 00:49:08.300 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: I believe so.

00:49:08.300 --> 00:49:14.510 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: --the spontaneous
experience that it is.

00:49:14.510 --> 00:49:17.870 align:middle line:90%
Each journey is unique.

00:49:17.870 --> 00:49:23.570 align:middle line:84%
And there shouldn't be anyone
who interferes with that.

00:49:23.570 --> 00:49:29.150 align:middle line:84%
There are no intermediaries
between you and your soul.

00:49:29.150 --> 00:49:30.650 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely not.

00:49:30.650 --> 00:49:32.460 align:middle line:84%
And yet everything
seems to intervene.

00:49:32.460 --> 00:49:36.950 align:middle line:84%
So, let's-- or interfere--
more so interfere.

00:49:36.950 --> 00:49:39.710 align:middle line:84%
So let's take our remaining
time and talk about some

00:49:39.710 --> 00:49:42.230 align:middle line:84%
of the ways in which
you suggest to people

00:49:42.230 --> 00:49:45.300 align:middle line:90%
they can begin this process.

00:49:45.300 --> 00:49:50.330 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Well when you
consider the fact that most

00:49:50.330 --> 00:49:58.430 align:middle line:10%
people spend more time with
self-maintenance, let's say,

00:49:58.430 --> 00:50:02.330 align:middle line:10%
than they do on cultivating
their connection

00:50:02.330 --> 00:50:06.290 align:middle line:10%
to their own soul, or
they spend much more time

00:50:06.290 --> 00:50:07.850 align:middle line:10%
watching television,
or maybe they

00:50:07.850 --> 00:50:11.510 align:middle line:10%
spend much more time
on their iPhone,

00:50:11.510 --> 00:50:16.170 align:middle line:10%
we can see right now that
we have a lot of work to do.

00:50:16.170 --> 00:50:19.280 align:middle line:10%
We have to shift our focus.

00:50:19.280 --> 00:50:23.060 align:middle line:10%
If we're going to pull the
bow up out of the water

00:50:23.060 --> 00:50:28.100 align:middle line:10%
and save the ship, we have
to alter what we're creating.

00:50:28.100 --> 00:50:32.600 align:middle line:10%
We have to recognize that
we have a lot more to learn

00:50:32.600 --> 00:50:37.700 align:middle line:10%
about the invisible energies
that support life, that

00:50:37.700 --> 00:50:41.830 align:middle line:10%
are being severely affected
by what we're creating.

00:50:41.830 --> 00:50:44.570 align:middle line:90%


00:50:44.570 --> 00:50:47.930 align:middle line:10%
And I think if people
really understood

00:50:47.930 --> 00:50:53.270 align:middle line:10%
how energy worked,
how frequency works,

00:50:53.270 --> 00:51:03.140 align:middle line:10%
how we have the ability to
go beyond every problem that

00:51:03.140 --> 00:51:07.810 align:middle line:10%
has been presented
to us on the planet--

00:51:07.810 --> 00:51:10.840 align:middle line:10%
if they understood
the value of it,

00:51:10.840 --> 00:51:14.980 align:middle line:10%
I think maybe people might
recognize how important it

00:51:14.980 --> 00:51:20.800 align:middle line:10%
is to cultivate self-mastery.

00:51:20.800 --> 00:51:22.930 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And again,
I think your book

00:51:22.930 --> 00:51:25.810 align:middle line:84%
makes a very good argument
for the need to do that.

00:51:25.810 --> 00:51:26.980 align:middle line:90%
We absolutely must do that.

00:51:26.980 --> 00:51:29.890 align:middle line:84%
That is the salvation
of the beauty,

00:51:29.890 --> 00:51:32.300 align:middle line:84%
and potential future beauty,
of life on Earth, period.

00:51:32.300 --> 00:51:32.930 align:middle line:90%
There isn't anything else.

00:51:32.930 --> 00:51:33.820 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: That's
our only way out.

00:51:33.820 --> 00:51:34.130 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It's the only way
out of this consciousness.

00:51:34.130 --> 00:51:35.560 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: That's
our only way through.

00:51:35.560 --> 00:51:36.435 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:51:36.435 --> 00:51:40.410 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Every advanced
master has always taught

00:51:40.410 --> 00:51:41.810 align:middle line:90%
self-mastery--

00:51:41.810 --> 00:51:42.610 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:51:42.610 --> 00:51:45.459 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: --never that
you go-- you're never between--

00:51:45.459 --> 00:51:47.000 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Never
turning to externals.

00:51:47.000 --> 00:51:49.270 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: --turning
to external ways,

00:51:49.270 --> 00:51:52.910 align:middle line:84%
never turning to a priest, or
a guru, or a supposed master.

00:51:52.910 --> 00:51:56.290 align:middle line:10%
Someone who calls him
or herself a master

00:51:56.290 --> 00:51:58.780 align:middle line:10%
would never do that
if they understood

00:51:58.780 --> 00:52:00.640 align:middle line:10%
what self-mastery really was.

00:52:00.640 --> 00:52:04.540 align:middle line:84%
Self-mastery is
what Jesus taught.

00:52:04.540 --> 00:52:09.580 align:middle line:84%
That's why he was
taken off the planet.

00:52:09.580 --> 00:52:17.370 align:middle line:10%
He was dealt with by the
dispirited and the false ego

00:52:17.370 --> 00:52:22.720 align:middle line:10%
in its most dangerous
and sad form.

00:52:22.720 --> 00:52:26.930 align:middle line:84%
So when you come
to planet Earth,

00:52:26.930 --> 00:52:29.390 align:middle line:84%
and you begin to
teach self-mastery,

00:52:29.390 --> 00:52:33.970 align:middle line:84%
what you're really teaching
is self-empowerment.

00:52:33.970 --> 00:52:36.310 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Don't need
any middle men or women.

00:52:36.310 --> 00:52:39.040 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Well, look.

00:52:39.040 --> 00:52:44.770 align:middle line:84%
We see by simply looking at
the culture, the world culture,

00:52:44.770 --> 00:52:46.840 align:middle line:84%
they are not
interested in helping

00:52:46.840 --> 00:52:48.320 align:middle line:90%
people find their power.

00:52:48.320 --> 00:52:49.120 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: No.

00:52:49.120 --> 00:52:51.161 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: They would
rather remain in power.

00:52:51.161 --> 00:52:52.390 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right, exactly.

00:52:52.390 --> 00:52:53.350 align:middle line:90%
And so it's up to us.

00:52:53.350 --> 00:52:55.120 align:middle line:90%
It's up to authors like you.

00:52:55.120 --> 00:52:57.910 align:middle line:84%
It's up to all people
who are choosing

00:52:57.910 --> 00:53:03.140 align:middle line:84%
to put the message that this
journey has dire consequences.

00:53:03.140 --> 00:53:05.195 align:middle line:84%
To not take this journey
has dire consequences.

00:53:05.195 --> 00:53:08.260 align:middle line:90%


00:53:08.260 --> 00:53:09.910 align:middle line:84%
And I like the
fact that you spend

00:53:09.910 --> 00:53:12.080 align:middle line:84%
the bulk of your book
really looking at-- you

00:53:12.080 --> 00:53:14.020 align:middle line:90%
do have exercises in there.

00:53:14.020 --> 00:53:17.680 align:middle line:84%
But in truth, there are many,
many different ways for one

00:53:17.680 --> 00:53:19.910 align:middle line:90%
to find their path, right?

00:53:19.910 --> 00:53:24.050 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Yes, and
it's a personal path.

00:53:24.050 --> 00:53:28.330 align:middle line:10%
No one can really tell you
how to find self-mastery.

00:53:28.330 --> 00:53:32.020 align:middle line:10%
Self-mastery is
whole brain thinking.

00:53:32.020 --> 00:53:33.070 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:53:33.070 --> 00:53:35.500 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: And
if you understand

00:53:35.500 --> 00:53:42.610 align:middle line:10%
that your intellect is linear,
your soul or your higher self

00:53:42.610 --> 00:53:46.840 align:middle line:10%
is non-linear, the
two work together,

00:53:46.840 --> 00:53:55.000 align:middle line:10%
every great power in the
universe has polarity to it.

00:53:55.000 --> 00:54:01.090 align:middle line:10%
Polarities are meant to
work together, in harmony.

00:54:01.090 --> 00:54:02.807 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes, exactly.

00:54:02.807 --> 00:54:04.390 align:middle line:84%
They're not meant
to fight each other.

00:54:04.390 --> 00:54:05.190 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Yes.

00:54:05.190 --> 00:54:08.200 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Polarity's different
than polarization, absolutely.

00:54:08.200 --> 00:54:11.930 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: So without
polarity, life would not exist.

00:54:11.930 --> 00:54:12.730 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:54:12.730 --> 00:54:16.340 align:middle line:84%
Male, female-- there would be
nothing within the universe.

00:54:16.340 --> 00:54:18.610 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: So let's
imagine that we're only

00:54:18.610 --> 00:54:20.350 align:middle line:90%
working with the intellect.

00:54:20.350 --> 00:54:22.300 align:middle line:90%
That's a partial equation.

00:54:22.300 --> 00:54:25.926 align:middle line:84%
We're working with
a partial equation.

00:54:25.926 --> 00:54:29.050 align:middle line:84%
We want to create
a whole equation

00:54:29.050 --> 00:54:31.160 align:middle line:90%
of balance and harmony.

00:54:31.160 --> 00:54:35.860 align:middle line:84%
The way that that's done
is whole brain thinking.

00:54:35.860 --> 00:54:40.570 align:middle line:84%
And that's the path
to self-mastery.

00:54:40.570 --> 00:54:43.390 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Absolutely, any
which way a person can find it.

00:54:43.390 --> 00:54:47.390 align:middle line:84%
But number one, it seems to me
it always starts in one place.

00:54:47.390 --> 00:54:50.390 align:middle line:84%
Just like when you read your
book, the points you make,

00:54:50.390 --> 00:54:53.180 align:middle line:84%
and arguments you
make for this needing

00:54:53.180 --> 00:54:57.160 align:middle line:84%
to be our top priority now, for
one-- top priority especially

00:54:57.160 --> 00:54:58.960 align:middle line:84%
