by family, by-- even there are
some systems that might even

00:55:03.140 --> 00:55:06.680 align:middle line:84%
create that, but
mostly by family--

00:55:06.680 --> 00:55:10.700 align:middle line:84%
is that we start
in simple places.

00:55:10.700 --> 00:55:13.060 align:middle line:84%
There are very simple
places to begin.

00:55:13.060 --> 00:55:14.680 align:middle line:90%
A, choice.

00:55:14.680 --> 00:55:15.700 align:middle line:90%
We're making a choice--

00:55:15.700 --> 00:55:16.480 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Free will.

00:55:16.480 --> 00:55:18.220 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yes, we're
using our free will.

00:55:18.220 --> 00:55:21.270 align:middle line:84%
And will has meaning
to make a choice

00:55:21.270 --> 00:55:23.230 align:middle line:84%
that this is our path
now, and that we're

00:55:23.230 --> 00:55:27.760 align:middle line:84%
going to spend some time each
day in reading one of the 1,000

00:55:27.760 --> 00:55:30.550 align:middle line:84%
books toward
self-mastery, right--

00:55:30.550 --> 00:55:32.180 align:middle line:90%
some better than others.

00:55:32.180 --> 00:55:35.600 align:middle line:84%
Or by simply honoring
simple principles inside,

00:55:35.600 --> 00:55:39.050 align:middle line:84%
like maybe start
with just compassion.

00:55:39.050 --> 00:55:39.850 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Yes.

00:55:39.850 --> 00:55:42.155 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Simple things--
beauty, generosity, peace.

00:55:42.155 --> 00:55:43.863 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Yes,
the fruits of spirit.

00:55:43.863 --> 00:55:44.720 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Exactly.

00:55:44.720 --> 00:55:46.350 align:middle line:84%
>>L'ESPERANCE: I'll tell
you a quick little story.

00:55:46.350 --> 00:55:46.750 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes?

00:55:46.750 --> 00:55:49.041 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: I recently
explained to a friend of mine

00:55:49.041 --> 00:55:56.470 align:middle line:10%
how I found the healing
retreat that I do work at.

00:55:56.470 --> 00:56:02.180 align:middle line:10%
And it is that a lavender
and white colored dragonfly

00:56:02.180 --> 00:56:05.680 align:middle line:10%
appeared in the window
of a realtor's office.

00:56:05.680 --> 00:56:07.660 align:middle line:84%
And I would have never
gone in had it not

00:56:07.660 --> 00:56:08.790 align:middle line:90%
been for that dragonfly.

00:56:08.790 --> 00:56:10.750 align:middle line:90%
Because it was a hot summer day.

00:56:10.750 --> 00:56:13.510 align:middle line:84%
And I said to myself,
that dragonfly is going

00:56:13.510 --> 00:56:16.990 align:middle line:90%
to die if I don't get it out.

00:56:16.990 --> 00:56:19.360 align:middle line:90%
I went inside.

00:56:19.360 --> 00:56:21.430 align:middle line:10%
I would have never gone.

00:56:21.430 --> 00:56:26.680 align:middle line:84%
And when I told that story
to my friend, he said,

00:56:26.680 --> 00:56:28.960 align:middle line:90%
I have to be more open.

00:56:28.960 --> 00:56:34.150 align:middle line:10%
I have to be more open to
these little, subtle, spiritual

00:56:34.150 --> 00:56:37.700 align:middle line:10%
signals in my life.

00:56:37.700 --> 00:56:40.917 align:middle line:84%
And you know, sometimes that's
all it is, is just opening--

00:56:40.917 --> 00:56:42.250 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Is just that, exactly.

00:56:42.250 --> 00:56:45.830 align:middle line:10%
>>L'ESPERANCE: --opening your
mind, opening your heart,

00:56:45.830 --> 00:56:52.750 align:middle line:10%
recognizing that life is a
miraculously, extraordinarily,

00:56:52.750 --> 00:56:54.500 align:middle line:10%
intelligent teacher.

00:56:54.500 --> 00:56:55.300 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: It is.

00:56:55.300 --> 00:57:00.029 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes it's the dragonfly
experience that gives you--

00:57:00.029 --> 00:57:02.320 align:middle line:84%
and what comes from that--
that gives that little point

00:57:02.320 --> 00:57:03.392 align:middle line:90%
of validation.

00:57:03.392 --> 00:57:04.850 align:middle line:84%
And if people are
paying attention,

00:57:04.850 --> 00:57:07.430 align:middle line:84%
they'll start seeing that
there's validation everywhere.

00:57:07.430 --> 00:57:08.230 align:middle line:90%
>>L'ESPERANCE: Yes.

00:57:08.230 --> 00:57:10.700 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Because we, as a
species, need that reassurance.

00:57:10.700 --> 00:57:11.600 align:middle line:90%
